Mxolisi Mgojo

Director
Mr. Mgojo was appointed to Tronox Board of Directors in June 2016.  He currently serves as the Chief Executive Officer of Exxaro Resources. He was appointed to this position on April 1, 2016. He was previously at Eyesizwe Coal, where he was responsible for marketing and logistics. Before assuming his current position as CEO, he was responsible for Exxaro’s base metals and industrial minerals commodity business. Mr. Mgojo holds a Bachelor of Science Degree in Energy Studies and received Master’s Degree in Business from the Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania.



  




