Maudi Lentsoane
Dr Bello Moussa
Niyi Akinmolayan




Mxolisi Mgojo has been appointed to serve as the CEO designate of Exxaro Resources. 
Mgojo serves as an Executive Head of Carbon Operations at Exxaro Resources Limited.  
Mgojo served as an Executive Head of Coal at Exxaro Resources Limited since August 2008 and served as its Executive Head of Operations. 
He served as an Executive General Manager of Coal at Exxaro Resources Limited since August 2008. He served as an Executive General Manager of Base Metals and Industrial Minerals of Exxaro Resources Limited. 
Previously, Mgojo served as Head of group marketing of Eyesizwe Coal. 
He serves as Director of Glen Douglas Dolomite (Pty) Limited, Exxaro Base Metals (Pty) Limited, Exxaro Ferroalloys and Alloystream (Pty) Limited. 
He serves as a Director of Richards Bay Coal Terminal Co Ltd. 
Mgojo holdan Advanced Management Programme from Wharton.
Mgojo holds an MBA from Henley.
